Comment: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂! 我說你!!
Comment: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:01:41.36,0:01:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是什麼人!!
Comment: 0,0:01:43.00,0:01:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自希干希納區的阿爾敏．亞魯雷特!
Comment: 0,0:01:46.12,0:01:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是嗎? 像是白癡一樣的名字呢!
Comment: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是父母親為你取的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:01:49.42,0:01:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是爺爺為我取的!
Comment: 0,0:01:51.30,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,亞魯雷特!
Comment: 0,0:01:52.32,0:01:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是為了什麼而來到這裡?
Comment: 0,0:01:54.12,0:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了給人類的生存盡一臂之力!
Comment: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這可真是太好了呢
Comment: 0,0:01:58.06,0:01:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就讓你成為巨人的食物吧!!
Comment: 0,0:01:59.98,0:02:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第三列 向後轉!
Comment: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是什麼人?
Comment: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:02:05.64,0:02:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自托洛斯特的托瑪斯．瓦格納
Comment: 0,0:02:07.87,0:02:08.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,太小聲了!!
Comment: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.36,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自托洛斯特的托...
Comment: 0,0:02:10.36,0:02:10.90,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,聽不到!
Comment: 0,0:02:10.74,0:02:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又來了...
Comment: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你還是訓練兵的時候也時常那樣對吧
Comment: 0,0:02:15.85,0:02:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還真懷念
Comment: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.85,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,我的名字是米娜．卡羅萊納!
Comment: 0,0:02:17.40,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對!
Comment: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是豬窩出生比家畜還不如的存在!
Comment: 0,0:02:20.65,0:02:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的 我比家畜還不如!
Comment: 0,0:02:22.88,0:02:24.22,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對!
Comment: 0,0:02:26.10,0:02:26.57,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,是!
Comment: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種恫嚇有什麼意義嗎?
Comment: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那是種過程儀式
Comment: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,將到目前為止的自己否定掉
Comment: 0,0:02:28.86,0:02:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從一無所有的狀態下 培育出適合擔任士兵的人材
Comment: 0,0:02:33.35,0:02:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為此 這是必經的路程
Comment: 0,0:02:35.32,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了人類而奉獻此身!
Comment: 0,0:02:37.57,0:02:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,第四列向後轉
Comment: 0,0:02:40.81,0:02:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,似乎有沒被叫到的人
Comment: 0,0:02:44.04,0:02:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經有過體驗的人就不需要了
Comment: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恐怕是兩年前那些見過真正地獄的人吧
Comment: 0,0:02:52.16,0:02:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,神情就是與他人不同
Comment: 0,0:02:54.41,0:02:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼 走吧
Comment: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是什麼人?
Comment: 0,0:02:58.30,0:03:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自托洛斯特區的約翰．基爾休坦!
Comment: 0,0:03:00.77,0:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是為了什麼而來到這裡?
Comment: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了進入憲兵團 到內地生活
Comment: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊
Comment: 0,0:03:09.69,0:03:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你這傢伙想去內地是吧
Comment: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的
Comment: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,痛...
Comment: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是誰准你坐下的?
Comment: 0,0:03:16.60,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在這裡就弱掉的人
Comment: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,有辦法進入憲兵團嗎?
Comment: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是什麼人!
Comment: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了什麼而來到這裡!
Comment: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自羅塞之牆南部吉納耶町的馬可．波特!
Comment: 0,0:03:27.52,0:03:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了進入憲兵團替國王服務獻身而來到這裡
Comment: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是嗎...
Comment: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這真是夠了
Comment: 0,0:03:35.73,0:03:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你大可以此為目標沒關係
Comment: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是...
Comment: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,國王可一點都不想要你的身體
Comment: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,下一個是你!
Comment: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是什麼人?
Comment: 0,0:03:48.74,0:03:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,柯尼．史普林格!
Comment: 0,0:03:49.80,0:03:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自羅塞之牆南部的拉加哥村!
Comment: 0,0:03:53.28,0:03:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,反了吧 柯尼．史普林格
Comment: 0,0:03:56.05,0:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我應該一開始就教過你才對
Comment: 0,0:03:58.01,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這敬禮的意義是在於展現「將心臟獻出」的決心
Comment: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你的心臟是在右邊嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 妳這傢伙...
Comment: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳在做什麼...
Comment: 0,0:04:23.56,0:04:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是妳! 我說的就是妳!!
Comment: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳又是什麼人!
Comment: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自羅塞之牆南部陶帕村的莎夏．布勞斯!
Comment: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,莎夏．布勞斯...
Comment: 0,0:04:36.57,0:04:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳右手上握著的是什麼?
Comment: 0,0:04:39.65,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是蒸過的馬鈴薯!
Comment: 0,0:04:41.39,0:04:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在廚房正好看到可以吃的東西
Comment: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不知不覺就...
Comment: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳這傢伙是用偷的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼...
Comment: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳為什麼在這時候吃馬鈴薯?
Comment: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為冷掉就不好了
Comment: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我判斷應該要現在就吃掉
Comment: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不...
Comment: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不懂啊...
Comment: 0,0:05:00.82,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為什麼妳這傢伙吃了馬鈴薯?
Comment: 0,0:05:04.81,0:05:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是指說「為什麼人要吃馬鈴薯」是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:05:23.68,0:05:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一半... 給你...
Comment: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,一... 半...
Comment: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 那個馬鈴薯女孩還在跑欸
Comment: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真厲害
Comment: 0,0:05:39.06,0:05:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,已經跑五個小時了
Comment: 0,0:05:41.05,0:05:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是比起被處罰「跑到快死為止」
Comment: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她聽到「今天沒飯吃」的瞬間感覺更驚訝呢
Comment: 0,0:05:49.19,0:05:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我記得陶帕村是在深山裡的少數民族對吧
Comment: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個呢?
Comment: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是退出的人唷
Comment: 0,0:05:58.47,0:06:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是自願移去開墾區的人
Comment: 0,0:06:00.82,0:06:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎麼這樣 還只是第一天耶
Comment: 0,0:06:03.98,0:06:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這也是沒辦法的
Comment: 0,0:06:05.41,0:06:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有力量的人只好離開
Comment: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒想到他們還想回到撿石除草的工作上
Comment: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,話說 你似乎沒有被問到來自哪裡
Comment: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,跟他一樣
Comment: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自希干希納區
Comment: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是這樣啊
Comment: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊
Comment: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說 「那一天」你也在對吧?
Comment: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 你有看過是嗎「超大型巨人」
Comment: 0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,呃... 嗯...
Comment: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就說了 我有看過...
Comment: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是真的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是有多大啊?
Comment: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大概是可以從城牆上露出臉來
Comment: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼!? 我可是聽說可以跨越城牆
Comment: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也是
Comment: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在我的村莊裡也是這樣說的
Comment: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不... 沒有到那麼大
Comment: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼臉長怎樣?
Comment: 0,0:06:54.18,0:06:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幾乎沒有皮膚而且嘴巴很大
Comment: 0,0:06:58.07,0:07:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,突破瑪利亞之牆的「盔甲巨人」呢?
Comment: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然大家都這樣叫
Comment: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在我眼裡看起來不過是普通的巨人
Comment: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那...那麼 普通的巨人呢?
Comment: 0,0:07:17.08,0:07:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家 不要再問了...
Comment: 0,0:07:20.04,0:07:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人家也有不願回想起來的事情吧
Comment: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉 讓你想起...
Comment: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不對!
Comment: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,其實巨人也沒有很了不起
Comment: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要我們能將立體機動裝置運用自如
Comment: 0,0:07:36.78,0:07:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那種東西根本算不上敵人
Comment: 0,0:07:38.88,0:07:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總算能夠以士兵的身份受訓了
Comment: 0,0:07:42.02,0:07:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剛才我也只是一時很有感覺而已
Comment: 0,0:07:44.87,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要進入調查兵團
Comment: 0,0:07:46.90,0:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把巨人從這世界上剷除 將他們殺光
Comment: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,欸欸... 你瘋了嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:07:53.13,0:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你剛剛說你想進入調查兵團是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是沒錯啊
Comment: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我記得 你說你想進入憲兵團偷閒是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可是老實人呢
Comment: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,比起心裡其實很害怕卻要裝的人
Comment: 0,0:08:10.16,0:08:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我應該相當爽朗才是
Comment: 0,0:08:13.01,0:08:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊?
Comment: 0,0:08:13.79,0:08:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是在說我嗎?
Comment: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,住手啦...
Comment: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂喂
Comment: 0,0:08:18.54,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我又沒有要...
Comment: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好啦 我錯了啦
Comment: 0,0:08:31.96,0:08:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我並不是要否定你的想法
Comment: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我們用這個來和好吧!
Comment: 0,0:08:38.89,0:08:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊 我也有不對
Comment: 0,0:08:56.47,0:08:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個 我說妳啊...
Comment: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那...那個... 這個...
Comment: 0,0:09:03.01,0:09:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想說沒有看過妳才...
Comment: 0,0:09:05.39,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不知不覺就...
Comment: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱...抱歉...
Comment: 0,0:09:08.78,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,黑色的頭髮非常漂亮
Comment: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,謝謝
Comment: 0,0:09:21.89,0:09:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,夠了吧 別管我啦
Comment: 0,0:09:24.13,0:09:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,火氣一上來 你就會立刻太過衝動
Comment: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,又說那種話...
Comment: 0,0:09:29.07,0:09:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,比起這個 我說妳啊
Comment: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,頭髮會不會太長啊...
Comment: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在立體機動的訓練時可能會出事哦
Comment: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我知道了...
Comment: 0,0:09:38.02,0:09:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,剪掉吧
Comment: 0,0:09:39.51,0:09:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是要剪到哪裡才...
Comment: 0,0:09:47.06,0:09:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 我說你 幹嘛摸別人的背?
Comment: 0,0:09:49.81,0:09:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你塗了什麼!?
Comment: 0,0:09:53.26,0:09:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抹掉了人與人之間的...
Comment: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,信賴...
Comment: 0,0:09:59.76,0:10:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,結束了...
Comment: 0,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個是...
Comment: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,麵包!!
Comment: 0,0:10:25.22,0:10:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只剩下這個 我就把它留了下來...
Comment: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是... 妳還是先喝水...
Comment: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳是神嗎!?
Comment: 0,0:10:38.49,0:10:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳是... 神啊!!!
Comment: 0,0:10:41.02,0:10:41.53,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:10:41.97,0:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳們在做什麼啊?
Comment: 0,0:10:45.26,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個...
Comment: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我看她到剛剛為止一直在跑步...
Comment: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳... 是想要「做好事」是吧?
Comment: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,什麼?
Comment: 0,0:10:59.58,0:11:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳這是為了馬鈴薯女而做的嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳得到的東西與勞力成正比嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:09.54,0:11:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,算了...
Comment: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總之先把她扛到床上去吧
Comment: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳也是「做好事」是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:11:19.25,0:11:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是為了讓她欠我一份人情
Comment: 0,0:11:22.51,0:11:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我很看好她的這股傻勁
Comment: 0,0:11:29.61,0:11:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,首先我要看看你們的合適度
Comment: 0,0:11:32.21,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,做不到的人 連當誘餌的資格都沒有!
Comment: 0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我會將他送往開墾區
Comment: 0,0:11:38.90,0:11:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這只不過是基礎中的基礎
Comment: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從這個階段就可以看出「立體機動」的素質了
Comment: 0,0:11:45.14,0:11:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 你看...
Comment: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,完全不會晃動
Comment: 0,0:11:49.92,0:11:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,她完全知道該怎麼做
Comment: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這就是所謂的資質
Comment: 0,0:11:56.98,0:11:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,今年看來有很多優秀的人
Comment: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個 那他呢...?
Comment: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那也是所謂的素質吧
Comment: 0,0:12:05.67,0:12:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是有足夠的氣魄...
Comment: 0,0:12:07.97,0:12:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也會有比一般人還差的情況
Comment: 0,0:12:11.32,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你在搞三小! 艾連．葉卡!!
Comment: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,把上半身給穩住!
Comment: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是怎樣...
Comment: 0,0:12:17.76,0:12:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這個到底要怎樣才...
Comment: 0,0:12:20.47,0:12:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,屁啦...
Comment: 0,0:12:32.88,0:12:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,CM
Comment: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要照著基本原則去做 應該就沒問題
Comment: 0,0:12:37.78,0:12:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不用想說要把它做到最好
Comment: 0,0:12:40.31,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,注意好前後的平衡
Comment: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,慢慢地讓腰間跟腳底的皮帶承受全身的重量
Comment: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要冷靜下來一定辦得到的
Comment: 0,0:12:48.57,0:12:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,連我都可以辦到了
Comment: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,好 我覺得這次應該可以成功
Comment: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幫我往上拉吧 阿爾敏
Comment: 0,0:12:55.03,0:12:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:13:10.21,0:13:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個 達茲
Comment: 0,0:13:11.60,0:13:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我記得那傢伙不是昨天說要把巨人全部殺光的人嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:17.42,0:13:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,想必明天一定會被送回開墾區吧
Comment: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,廢物可是沒有飯吃的
Comment: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連
Comment: 0,0:13:24.76,0:13:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你想再多也是沒用的
Comment: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只要明天把它學會就好了
Comment: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:30.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真是丟臉
Comment: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣... 怎麼可能把他們給剷除...
Comment: 0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不該再以這個為目標
Comment: 0,0:13:38.59,0:13:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳說什麼?
Comment: 0,0:13:40.20,0:13:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我是說你不該以當上士兵為目標
Comment: 0,0:13:43.25,0:13:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是只有拚上性命才叫戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說妳... 我可是在「那一天」看到了那樣子的景象
Comment: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,妳以為這樣子的理由就能夠說服我嗎?
Comment: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 這跟你的決心無關
Comment: 0,0:13:57.66,0:13:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊? 為什麼?
Comment: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,因為判斷能不能成為士兵的
Comment: 0,0:14:02.78,0:14:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是艾連你來判斷的
Comment: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不是要艾連你自己回開墾區
Comment: 0,0:14:12.46,0:14:13.16,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,走吧
Comment: 0,0:14:13.83,0:14:15.05,Upside,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯...
Comment: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你不需要擔心
Comment: 0,0:14:18.35,0:14:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候 我也會跟你一起去的
Comment: 0,0:14:26.59,0:14:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個...
Comment: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說...
Comment: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我可以拿走它是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你是說控制姿勢的訣竅?
Comment: 0,0:14:53.75,0:14:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉 我是個天才
Comment: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我只能說憑感覺
Comment: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我倒是希望你能教教我
Comment: 0,0:15:00.11,0:15:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,怎樣在出了那樣的糗後 還能夠保持冷靜的訣竅
Comment: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我說你們... 我可是低下頭來請求你們耶
Comment: 0,0:15:08.93,0:15:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是 你昨天說了「沒有力量的人就該走」不是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊 說錯了
Comment: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有才能的人就該走是吧?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是哪一個啊?
Comment: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,拜託了 我聽說你們兩位都很厲害
Comment: 0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,貝爾托特... 萊納...
Comment: 0,0:15:28.08,0:15:29.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,很抱歉...
Comment: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我不認為光是垂掛需要什麼訣竅
Comment: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,恐怕無法給你 你所期待的建議
Comment: 0,0:15:35.50,0:15:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊
Comment: 0,0:15:36.67,0:15:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,看來只能賭明天了
Comment: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們兩個... 那個... 都是來自希干希納區對吧?
Comment: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是這樣沒錯
Comment: 0,0:15:46.04,0:15:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼 你們應該也知道巨人的可怕
Comment: 0,0:15:49.35,0:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,可是 為何還要來當士兵呢?
Comment: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟艾連不同 沒有直接感受到巨人的恐怖所在
Comment: 0,0:16:00.23,0:16:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是... 一想到國家執行那種魯莽的反攻行動
Comment: 0,0:16:06.14,0:16:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我就無法放著不管
Comment: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這樣啊...
Comment: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們兩個是來自哪裡?
Comment: 0,0:16:12.72,0:16:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟萊納都是
Comment: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,來自瑪利亞之牆東南方深山裡的村子
Comment: 0,0:16:17.67,0:16:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,等... 那是...
Comment: 0,0:16:19.78,0:16:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,啊 跟河岸邊的城市不一樣
Comment: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒有立刻就收到巨人來的聯絡通知
Comment: 0,0:16:26.09,0:16:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,應該說 因為巨人比消息更早到
Comment: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那時候是清晨
Comment: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,家畜非常地吵雜
Comment: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒聽過的地鳴愈來愈大聲
Comment: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不知何時發現這是某種腳步聲
Comment: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,然後 我趕緊將窗戶一開...
Comment: 0,0:16:56.79,0:17:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,之後的事情... 怎麼說... 我不太記得了
Comment: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,大家非常驚惶失措
Comment: 0,0:17:03.90,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂 為什麼突然聊起這個?
Comment: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,抱歉
Comment: 0,0:17:09.05,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說 我想說的是
Comment: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你們應該跟「他們」不同才對
Comment: 0,0:17:16.12,0:17:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「他們」?
Comment: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就是在這裡其他不知道巨人的可怕的人
Comment: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,喂
Comment: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,「他們」會在這裡大多數的理由是
Comment: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了保住世間的評價
Comment: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,加上12歲成為生產者的人都被說成膽小鬼
Comment: 0,0:17:38.20,0:17:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,最後因為輿論的關係而淪落為訓練兵
Comment: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,就算是這樣
Comment: 0,0:17:43.63,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我跟他們沒兩樣
Comment: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,為了在安全的內陸值勤 以憲兵團為目標
Comment: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,而選擇當上士兵
Comment: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果真的不行 我可能會全都放棄
Comment: 0,0:17:55.95,0:17:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,對我而言 我沒有自己的想法
Comment: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,珍惜自己的生命也是很棒的事情
Comment: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,要回去已經回不去的故鄉
Comment: 0,0:18:11.63,0:18:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我心裡只有這個
Comment: 0,0:18:15.24,0:18:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,絕對要回去 無論如何
Comment: 0,0:18:20.18,0:18:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你呢?
Comment: 0,0:18:22.67,0:18:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你為什麼要成為士兵?
Comment: 0,0:18:26.92,0:18:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...
Comment: 0,0:18:33.09,0:18:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,只是覺得不殺了他們不行
Comment: 0,0:18:36.38,0:18:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我要用這雙手將巨人趕盡殺絕
Comment: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我這樣想著
Comment: 0,0:18:47.30,0:18:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說即便你遭遇過巨人
Comment: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也沒有因此屈服 是嗎?
Comment: 0,0:18:51.81,0:18:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯
Comment: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不過現在問題是能不能成為士兵這點
Comment: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你就從重新調整皮帶開始嘗試吧
Comment: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,明天會順利的
Comment: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如果是你的話應該辦得到
Comment: 0,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你叫艾連．葉卡 對吧
Comment: 0,0:19:28.08,0:19:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,嗯 謝謝
Comment: 0,0:19:30.66,0:19:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你叫萊納．布朗 對吧
Comment: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連．葉卡
Comment: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你做好覺悟了嗎?
Comment: 0,0:19:46.03,0:19:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的!
Comment: 0,0:19:47.33,0:19:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我辦得到
Comment: 0,0:19:48.50,0:19:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我辦得到的
Comment: 0,0:19:50.52,0:19:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,或許我沒有什麼資質
Comment: 0,0:19:53.50,0:19:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是毅力是不會輸給任何人的
Comment: 0,0:19:57.07,0:19:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,開始
Comment: 0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我才不管什麼原理
Comment: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也毫無根據
Comment: 0,0:20:09.94,0:20:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但是... 我也只能靠它
Comment: 0,0:20:13.89,0:20:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這就是我的武器!
Comment: 0,0:20:21.35,0:20:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,辦到了
Comment: 0,0:20:22.85,0:20:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成功了
Comment: 0,0:20:33.57,0:20:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還沒...
Comment: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還沒...
Comment: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我還沒...
Comment: 0,0:20:39.69,0:20:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,放他下來
Comment: 0,0:20:45.69,0:20:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我...我還沒...
Comment: 0,0:20:49.38,0:20:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,瓦格納
Comment: 0,0:20:50.51,0:20:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你跟葉卡交換皮帶的裝備
Comment: 0,0:20:52.61,0:20:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,是的!
Comment: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這是裝備的缺陷
Comment: 0,0:21:04.49,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,你所使用的皮帶扣環已經破損了
Comment: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,雖然我從來沒有聽過這裡會破損
Comment: 0,0:21:12.06,0:21:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,但貌似有必要增加新的整備項目
Comment: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,也就是說 他用破損的裝備
Comment: 0,0:21:17.74,0:21:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,維持住身體?
Comment: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,真厲害
Comment: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那麼... 適合度的判斷如何?
Comment: 0,0:21:24.44,0:21:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,沒問題
Comment: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,繼續努力
Comment: 0,0:21:28.44,0:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,辦到了
Comment: 0,0:21:29.53,0:21:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我辦到了!
Comment: 0,0:21:31.32,0:21:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,如何啊 米卡莎
Comment: 0,0:21:32.76,0:21:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我辦得到的
Comment: 0,0:21:34.49,0:21:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,我也能夠跟巨人戰鬥
Comment: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,以後不會再給妳添麻煩了
Comment: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,總算是成功了啊
Comment: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他的眼神貌似在說「怎麼樣啊?」
Comment: 0,0:21:46.18,0:21:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,不是
Comment: 0,0:21:49.12,0:21:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,他只是想到這樣就不必跟我分開
Comment: 0,0:21:52.34,0:21:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,所以很放心而已
Comment: 0,0:21:57.16,0:22:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,古利夏 今天你兒子
Comment: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,成為士兵了
Comment: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,從訓練兵團中畢業的艾連
Comment: 0,0:23:59.22,0:24:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,眼中有著奪回人類尊嚴的樣子
Comment: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,能夠贏過巨人
Comment: 0,0:24:05.04,0:24:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,在他確信的瞬間
Comment: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,人類又再次體會到...
